<p class="zfr3Q" id="h.p_YIjAtgBc77IB">Boaz Barak, Shafi Goldwasser, Eli Ben Sasson, Gil Kalai, Yael Kalai, Guy Kindler, Elchanan Mossel, Christos Papadimitriou, Aviad Rubinstein, Ran Raz, Ronitt Rubinfeld, Oded Schwartz, Irit Dinur, Andrew Yao, and Avi Wigderson.</p>
